== Basic Tools

The most widely used tool for producing plots is Excel. However, Excel plots are recognisable from a mile away, and Excel makes choices for you in terms of the look of your plot that might not be the best. If you want to prepare good plots there are a number of tools that can either make your Excel plots look better or make better plots.  
    
